N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 9000.3 - Renumbered

State Regulations

Subsequent renumbering or renaming of any route, road or
location contained in any Part of Chapter VIII shall not affect the validity of
any regulation contained therein. Any reference to a route, road or location by
a name or number in existence at the time of promulgation of a regulation or
order shall be deemed to apply to such route, road or location even though such
route, road or location is subsequently renamed or
renumbered. Notes
